Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value:
BEGIN
declare @DBId int Set @DBId = (select Id from Company where Id = @Id)
if(@DBId is null) begin
INSERT INTO [dbo].Company (Name, CreatedTime) VALUES (@Name, GETDATE())
Set @DBId = @@IDENTITY end else begin
UPDATE [dbo].Company SET [Name] = @Name WHERE Id = @Id end
Select @DBId return @DBId END
